OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FWaste management company Biffa has
OL,7,Fsuggested a deposit scheme for vapes
OL,8,Fcould reduce littering.
OL,10,FIt comes as millions of vapes are
OL,11,Fstill being binned one year after the
OL,12,Fgovernment banned single-use devices,
OL,13,Faccording to councils and campaigners.
OL,15,FShops and online retailers can only
OL,16,Fsell vapes that meet a set of reusable
OL,17,Fcriteria after ministers introduced
OL,18,Fnew rules a year ago on Monday as part
OL,19,Fof efforts to crack down on their use
OL,20,Famong young people and environmental
OL,21,Fimpacts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FBut vape makers have since developed
OL,7,Fcheap, new styles that meet the legal
OL,8,Frequirements yet are sold, priced and
OL,9,Fused in the same way as the disposable
OL,10,Fmodels they replaced, meaning they
OL,11,Fessentially circumvent the ban.
OL,13,FLocal authorities are now among those
OL,14,Fcalling on the government to tighten
OL,15,Fthe legal definition of a single-use
OL,16,Fvape to include these products and
OL,17,Fwarn of gaps in information or access
OL,18,Ffor consumers when it comes to
OL,19,Frecycling points.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FBiffa, the UK's largest waste
OL,7,Fmanagement company, is requesting a
OL,8,Fscheme where consumers pay a small
OL,9,Fmandatory deposit when they purchase a
OL,10,Fvape.
OL,12,FThe fee would be redeemed when the
OL,13,Fdevice is safely returned to existing
OL,14,Ftake-back systems that should be
OL,15,Favailable at all vape retailers, under
OL,16,Fthe plan supported by the industry
OL,17,Ftrade body, the Environmental Services
OL,18,FAssociation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
