PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FThe calls to government come after
OL,7,Fresearch by campaign group Material
OL,8,FFocus estimated that the number of
OL,9,Fvapes and pods thrown away each week,
OL,10,Fbefore the ban, was around 8.2 million.
OL,12,FWhile this had decreased over the last
OL,13,Fyear, 6.3 million vapes and pods were
OL,14,Fstill discarded in the last year,
OL,15,Faccording to the group's findings,
OL,16,Fwhich were calculated from polling
OL,17,Fcarried out by Opinium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FAs part of the recent reforms,
OL,7,Fretailers are also required to offer
OL,8,Ftake-back and recycling facilities,
OL,9,Fhelping to cover the cost of vape
OL,10,Fcollections.
OL,12,FBut the Material Focus survey of 1,000
OL,13,Fadults who recently bought vapes found
OL,14,Fthat 47% were unaware they could be
OL,15,Frecycled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FThe poll also suggested that 43% of
OL,7,Fthose who tried to recycle vapes at
OL,8,Fsupermarkets were unable to find a
OL,9,Fcollection point, while 63% were
OL,10,Funable to at local convenience stores,
OL,11,Fand 33% were unable to at specialist
OL,12,Fvape retailers.
OL,14,FSeparate polling of 1,000 vape users,
OL,15,Fcarried out by Censuswide on behalf of
OL,16,Fconsumer safety charity Electrical
OL,17,FSafety First, found that more than
OL,18,Fhalf of vapers (59%) admitted to
OL,19,Fdisposing of their vapes incorrectly
OL,20,Fin household rubbish or recycling bins
OL,21,Fover the past 12 months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
