PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FData from Biffa showed that more than
OL,7,Ftwo million incorrectly discarded
OL,8,Fvapes were found at four of its sites
OL,9,Fbetween June 2025 and March this year.
OL,11,FThis equates to almost 300 vapes every
OL,12,Fhour and more than 6,500 every day at
OL,13,Fjust those sites.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
