PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FMeanwhile, fire chiefs said that
OL,7,Fblazes in bin lorries as well as
OL,8,Frecycling and waste centres continued
OL,9,Fthis year, often caused by lithium-ion
OL,10,Fbatteries in rechargeable vapes that
OL,11,Fspark when crushed or damaged.
OL,13,FThe Local Government Association
OL,14,F(LGA), which represents councils in
OL,15,FEngland and Wales, said they were
OL,16,Fbearing the cost of contaminated
OL,17,Frecycling and fires, which ultimately
OL,18,Ffell on residents through council tax
OL,19,Frather than on the producers and
OL,20,Fretailers who profited from vape sales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
