OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780398175
OL,3,CPutting a deposit on vapes would
OL,4,Creduce littering, waste companies say
OL,6,FAs well as tightening the statutory
OL,7,Fdefinition of single-use vapes, the
OL,8,FLGA said ministers must strengthen
OL,9,Fretail take-back schemes, increase the
OL,10,Ffees charged to producers to cover the
OL,11,Fsafe disposals, and deliver a public
OL,12,Fawareness campaign on the dangers of
OL,13,Fbinning vapes in household waste.
